{"ha7638fcage826g4715gb374gb7cee9fdfa20": ["I know you stopped the goblins, but I can't stop looking over my shoulder.", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "e93e9b52-c153-62f2-f53d-340cc9036844"], "h530e52e0g9d5fg4d4cga670g31430707f217": ["Makes it hard to sleep at night.", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "8ff67f9a-3a6c-7397-23f8-b2c5c37868fd"], "hce42317agae2cg4314ga7acg34d65b737ab2": ["I'm seeing goblins in every shadow.", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "0ebff57a-cd1b-d47a-6def-6e85c5615359"], "h34937f18g857bg4f10ga04fg886e43e77564": ["To think we almost finished the ritual...", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "c875c2f1-5cbc-044c-1ee5-c3fda95dd76d"], "hbabe4c6cgf537g44ecg96f7g4eddf0dfa182": ["I felt honoured when I was chosen to participate. Now I feel guilty I didn't object.", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "52743624-16c5-1b39-e0a1-7c2f29d25cbe"], "h66049658gbe6eg4468gb129g6f17c7567ff7": ["We thought we were doing the right thing.", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "ce42c240-c158-d9ab-de6e-7d511f6a5e59"], "h8bad0ef7g5d87g4010g8e3cg9db40d5c9ff5": ["<i>In umbram cretus, sanguine iuratus.</i>", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "39366622-9aff-fbac-d6ae-bbb85435b4b8"], "h04a0953bg5ce6g4cb0gad7age237d0fc9e90": ["<i>Ab spiritu humoque, aculeus vitisque.</i>", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "36d5dc53-45a6-6f2d-8e78-35ff3ffaf0ee"], "heb048648gf16ag4942g8de1g9c0375058bf8": ["<i>Complexum tuum, ab terra ortum, ad nos defer.</i>", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "7d26cf23-964d-0537-8784-83fcd01930f2"], "h7c9018fagf843g44cegb10bg62f61ceafec1": ["<i>Defende nos ab imminentibus aequilibrio tuo.</i>", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "74900cba-036a-aad3-f61f-2f857b309ba5"], "h60fa746agd7dfg4f96g9569g6db23cd5bf26": ["<i>Hostes subeunt. Protege nos. Muni nos.</i>", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "9ba300d4-37c3-01e4-409b-19a244952f44"], "h62f1a6ebgbcdfg43ebgbc3eg929b9df22098": ["<i>Aggeniculamur in umbra tua, Pater Arborum.</i>", "7cae8e24-d610-4229-859d-7b2da7c5d162", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_SacredPond_RitualDruid3.html", "a1ce761d-fa81-9147-1c6f-58107e34f165"]}